# Contexto R\u00e1pido \u2014 Brech\u00f3 na M\u00e3o

> **Lido PRIMEIRO por qualquer agente/IA em nova sess\u00e3o.**
> Se\u00e7\u00e3o atual: Tela 5 (Legenda). Refs: `STATE.md` para detalhes, `ROADMAP.md` para status.

## Projeto
- Web app mobile-first para gerar posts de Instagram de brech\u00f3
- Fluxo: tira foto do manequim \u2192 IA gera modelo virtual \u2192 adiciona texto \u2192 IA gera legenda \u2192 baixa imagem pronta
- **Persona:** tia 50-65 anos, usa Android Realme 360x800, Wi-Fi inst\u00e1vel, sem conhecimento t\u00e9cnico
- **Budget MVP:** R$ 0/m\u00eas
- **5 telas + integra\u00e7\u00e3o + deploy:** Upload \u2705 \u2192 Config \u2705 \u2192 Gera\u00e7\u00e3o \u2705 \u2192 Composi\u00e7\u00e3o \u2705 \u2192 Legenda \u23f3 \u2192 E2E \u23f3 \u2192 Deploy \u23f3

## Onde estamos (sess\u00e3o #2, 2026-06-28)
- **\u00daltima se\u00e7\u00e3o completa:** Tela 4 (Composi\u00e7\u00e3o) \u2014 tag `v0.5-tela-4-composicao`
- **Se\u00e7\u00e3o atual:** Tela 5 (Legenda) \u2014 **pr\u00f3xima a implementar**
- **Pr\u00f3xima se\u00e7\u00e3o:** Integra\u00e7\u00e3o E2E (fluxo completo)
- Branch: `main` (limpo, 17 commits, 5 tags)

## Stack travado (N\u00c3O mudar sem alinhamento)
- **Framework:** Next.js 16.2.9 (App Router) + React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind 4
- **Hosting:** Vercel Hobby (plano B: Cloudflare \u2014 ver `../docs/PESQUISA-CLOUDFLARE-PLANO-B.md`)
- **Banco:** Neon PostgreSQL (sa-east-1) + Prisma 7 (com `prisma.config.ts` separado)
- **Imagens:** Cloudinary (`dmqqkv4ru`, 25 credits/m\u00eas = ~25k transforma\u00e7\u00f5es)
- **VTON:** HF Spaces (Kolors-VTON primary, OutfitAnyone + OOTDiffusion fallback) \u2014 **AGORA REAL**
- **LLM (legendas):** Groq (Qwen3-32B, `gsk_...`) + Cerebras + OpenRouter fallback
- **Valida\u00e7\u00e3o:** Zod + react-hook-form
- **UI:** Componentes pr\u00f3prios (Button \u226548px, LgpdBanner, SizePills, ComposeForm, ComposedPreview)

## Decis\u00f5es importantes
- **Iago vai sozinho** (decis\u00e3o 22/06/2026)
- **Vercel Hobby** (decis\u00e3o 22/06/2026): R$ 0/m\u00eas, risco TOS assumido
- **Plano B Cloudflare** documentado caso Vercel reclame (~2 dias migra\u00e7\u00e3o)
- **Tela 4 (Composi\u00e7\u00e3o) \u2014 Cloudinary server-side overlay** (decis\u00e3o 28/06): 3 layers verticais (TAM + pre\u00e7o + rodap\u00e9), sem re-upload, parser de URL Cloudinary pra extrair publicId+version
- **VTON real (HF Spaces) AGORA FUNCIONA** \u2014 fetch HTTP direto pra API Gradio do Space, chain de fallback (Kolors \u2192 OutfitAnyone \u2192 OOTDiffusion), cold-start handling 30-60s, timeout 90s
- **Job VTON:** fire-and-forget + polling 3s + timeout 90s (Vercel Hobby aguenta 5 min)
- **Timeout do Vercel 2026:** 5 min, n\u00e3o 10s (corrigido)
- **Limite de 3 regen** hardcoded na Tela 3 (constante `MAX_REGENS` no `app/generate/page.tsx`)

## Arquivos cr\u00edticos j\u00e1 criados
- `prisma/schema.prisma` (Settings, Post, Generation) + migra\u00e7\u00e3o aplicada
- `prisma.config.ts` (Prisma 7+ com helper `env()`)
- `src/lib/db/prisma.ts` (singleton PrismaPg)
- `src/lib/cloudinary/client.ts` (uploadImage + **buildComposedUrl**)
- `src/lib/cloudinary/parsePublicId.ts` (extrai publicId+version de URL)
- `src/lib/groq/client.ts` (Qwen3-32B + fallback)
- `src/lib/huggingface/client.ts` (VTON + **callHFSpace REAL** com Gradio HTTP API)
- `src/lib/schemas/config.ts` (Zod: GARMENT_TYPES, SIZES, STYLES, `parsePriceString`)
- `src/lib/schemas/compose.ts` (Zod: composeRequestSchema, composeFormSchema)
- `src/lib/hooks/use-tryon.ts` (POST + polling + timeout)
- `src/lib/utils.ts` (cn, formatPrice, isValidUrl)
- `src/components/{ui,upload,config,generation,compose}/*` (10+ componentes)
- `src/app/{api,config,generate,compose}/` (5 API routes + 4 p\u00e1ginas)

## Vari\u00e1veis de ambiente (em `.env.local`, N\u00c3O vai pro git)
- `DATABASE_URL` (Neon pooled)
- `CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME`, `CLOUDINARY_API_KEY`, `CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET`
- `GROQ_API_KEY`, `GROQ_MODEL=qwen/qwen3-32b`
- `HF_TOKEN` (opcional)
- `VTON_PROVIDER=hf` (ou `fashn`)

## Pend\u00eancias conhecidas
- **callHFSpace() IMPLEMENTADO** \u2014 validar com imagem real quando for testar Tela 3
- **Cloudinary text overlay IMPLEMENTADO** \u2014 validar visualmente com imagem real
- **FASHN provider** n\u00e3o implementado (Fase 2 \u2014 pago)
- **Cerebras/OpenRouter fallback** n\u00e3o implementado (Tela 5)
- **LGPD banner** SSR flicker (mitiga\u00e7\u00e3o futura)
- **Testes E2E** n\u00e3o escritos

